  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/03495b5f72d8070a87a14f7578f384d3.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of our beloved Zookeeper, where chaos reigns supreme and every day is a wild adventure where your fluffy pals are not just cute—they're colossal!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From belly-surfing hippos to tool-attacking rabbits, each day brings new hilarious challenges that will have you laughing out loud and racing against the clock. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you keep the chaos under control and ensure your chubby friends have the time of their lives?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your Zookeeper hat and get your friends—let's get this party started!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/7631192f31654341e8cc77e4033a4c02.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=164 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/588e63a057827d55e5dcf1196fa786b3.poster.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/588e63a057827d55e5dcf1196fa786b3.webm?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/588e63a057827d55e5dcf1196fa786b3.mp4?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got friends? Great! Now you can all yell at each other while trying to wrangle a virtual hippo. Local AND Remote play? We're enabling your inner zoo-boss from anywhere!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/03bd1ba895a4e82b17475df75d187622.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/956e41c5036e12467f83329f99791b03.poster.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/956e41c5036e12467f83329f99791b03.webm?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/956e41c5036e12467f83329f99791b03.mp4?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From \"Couch Potato Chimp\" to \"Zoo Tycoon Titan,\" pick your poison! Each difficulty has its own progression, so you can start as a clueless newbie and become a zoo-managing mastermind... or just stick with the chimps. No judgement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/383565cef64698887999c0e0088a1307.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/dfb8b8a39f8b2d02a3aa63527460ba3a.poster.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/dfb8b8a39f8b2d02a3aa63527460ba3a.webm?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/dfb8b8a39f8b2d02a3aa63527460ba3a.mp4?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 cuddly critters, 40 brain-bending levels, and a to-do list that never ends! Think you can keep a zoo running smoothly? <strong>Spoiler alert</strong>: probably not. But it’ll be hilarious to watch you try!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/06ea17fe2f9ee093baa622e2cae50475.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/b5624e1f865d76af9447e35765eb4688.poster.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/b5624e1f865d76af9447e35765eb4688.webm?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/b5624e1f865d76af9447e35765eb4688.mp4?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you've mastered the zoo? Think again! Hidden mechanics and bonus objectives are lurking around every corner. Prepare to have your zookeeper mind blown ^^</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/03495b5f72d8070a87a14f7578f384d3.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of our beloved Zookeeper, where chaos reigns supreme and every day is a wild adventure where your fluffy pals are not just cute—they're colossal!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From belly-surfing hippos to tool-attacking rabbits, each day brings new hilarious challenges that will have you laughing out loud and racing against the clock. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you keep the chaos under control and ensure your chubby friends have the time of their lives?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your Zookeeper hat and get your friends—let's get this party started!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/7631192f31654341e8cc77e4033a4c02.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=164 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/588e63a057827d55e5dcf1196fa786b3.poster.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/588e63a057827d55e5dcf1196fa786b3.webm?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/588e63a057827d55e5dcf1196fa786b3.mp4?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got friends? Great! Now you can all yell at each other while trying to wrangle a virtu