ype=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/dfb8b8a39f8b2d02a3aa63527460ba3a.mp4?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 cuddly critters, 40 brain-bending levels, and a to-do list that never ends! Think you can keep a zoo running smoothly? <strong>Spoiler alert</strong>: probably not. But it’ll be hilarious to watch you try!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/06ea17fe2f9ee093baa622e2cae50475.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/b5624e1f865d76af9447e35765eb4688.poster.avif?t=1747688452\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/b5624e1f865d76af9447e35765eb4688.webm?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280100/extras/b5624e1f865d76af9447e35765eb4688.mp4?t=1747688452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you've mastered the zoo? Think again! Hidden mechanics and bonus objectives are lurking around every corner. Prepare to have your zookeeper mind blown ^^</p>",
